<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container mt-3 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Who can launch a project on Boomerang?</h2>
        <p>
            Project creation is available to individuals and organizations in Thailand who meet these criteria:
            <ul>
                <li>Age: 18 years or older.</li>
                <li>Residency: Permanent resident of Thailand.</li>
                <li>Identification: Valid address, bank account, and government-issued ID in Thailand.</li>
                <li>Financial: Possess a major credit or debit card.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">What if Boomerang isn't available in my country yet?</h2>
        <p>
            We're actively working to expand our platform to more countries. Stay tuned for updates.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">How does Boomerang support creators?</h2>
        <p>
            We provide tools and resources at every stage of your journey. Our Creator Resources offer insights and best practices to help you plan, promote, and fulfill your project successfully.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">How does all-or-nothing funding work?</h2>
        <p>
            Backers are only charged if your project reaches its funding goal within the set timeframe. This ensures you have the full budget needed to bring your idea to life.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">Who can support my project?</h2>
        <p>
            Support often begins with friends, family, and fans. As your project gains momentum, word spreads, and more people who share your passion will join in.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">What are the fees?</h2>
        <p>
            Upon successful funding, Boomerang applies a 5% fee to the funds raised. Our payment processor, 2C2P, also applies standard processing fees. No fees are collected if your project doesn't reach its goal.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 text-primary mb-3">What kinds of projects can I launch on Boomerang?</h2>
        <p>
            Boomerang supports creative projects across categories like art, design, technology, music, and film. We also support non-profit fundraisers and charitable causes in a dedicated section.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>
